headline: GrowthLoop Launches Compound Marketing Engine for Commerce Media Networks, Enabling Enterprises to Unlock New Revenue Streams
summary: GrowthLoop, a pioneer in AI-driven marketing innovation, today unveiled its new, purpose-built solution for commerce media teams: Compound Marketing Engine for Commerce Media Networks. This solution, built on top of the GrowthLoop composable core, enables enterprises to scale high-margin commerce media operations quickly and securely using their first-party data.

headline: Ka'Chava Expands Its Retail Presence with Exclusive Launch on Costco.com
summary: Ka'Chava, the whole body meal for whole body health, has officially launched on Costco.com, bringing its plant-based superfood shakes to Costco shoppers nationwide. For the first time ever, members can now purchase Ka'Chava's best-selling Chocolate shake in a 30-serving bag – the brand's largest size and best value at $89.99 ($3 per serving, Ka'Chava's best value yet) – available exclusively on Costco.com for a limited time.
